With one eye opened and one eye closed, Miriam wobbles to the sink. The icy chill of splashed water on her face sends chills down her spine and banishes any sleep that lingered. <br>
<br>
&quot;Saeran??&quot; <br>
<br>
A groan answers her from her bedroom. Good boy. Placing a hand against her temple she grinds her teeth. @#%$ hangovers... <br>
