<br>
&quot;We should get more sleep first, hun. My head is still throbbing, and I'm sure yours is too. So lets get our stanky butts back into bed before we fall and hurt ourselves&quot; <br>
<br>
With a giggle and a tug she was pulling him back to her bedroom. Bursting through the door she hops onto her bed and lays on her back smilling. Yesturday was fun. Nothing could make her frown quite like Caelestis, but nothing could make her smile quite like Saeran. Turning on her side she snuggles into a pillow. Sighing happily, Miriam drifts off to sleep.<br>
